name: Orange and Purple
content: ORANGE AND PURPLE from @barmaxla and @tipsybartender 🙏🏻 This is a unique cocktail featuring @whistlepigwhiskey🥃👌🏻 1 ½ oz. (45ml) @whistlepigwhiskey 1 ½ oz. (45ml) Tangerine Liqueur 1 ½ oz. (45ml) Strega (Herbal Liqueur) 2 drops Balsamic Vinegar Ube Foam [cooked and mashed Ube, egg white, sugar, vanilla extract, lemon juice, whiskey] Flower Garnish • PREPARATION 1. In a mixing glass with ice, combine rye whiskey, tangerine liqueur, herbal liqueur, and two drops of balsamic vinegar. Stir well.2. In a whipped cream canister, combine mashed cooked ube, an egg white, sugar, vanilla extract, lemon juice, and whiskey. Shake and charge.3. Strain the mix into a serving glass over ice and top with the ube foam. 4. Garnish with flowers of your preference. Cheers!
